01:07:05.847 --> 01:07:08.763
[FRANKIE HOLLERS, PANTS]

01:07:08.894 --> 01:07:10.417
Fuck you!

01:07:10.548 --> 01:07:12.767
Agh! Agh!

01:07:12.854 --> 01:07:14.291
[SHUDDERS]

01:07:14.421 --> 01:07:17.163
BEN: It was like the switch
