Frank.

01:07:47.759 --> 01:07:49.239
[MUFFLED GROANING]

01:07:49.369 --> 01:07:51.067
Shh.

01:07:52.416 --> 01:07:53.808
[SHELL CASING CLINKS ON FLOOR]

01:07:55.854 --> 01:07:59.510
BEN: I'd never met
any of Abe's personalities,

01:07:59.640 --> 01:08:01.903
