who this was.

01:08:03.383 --> 01:08:05.037
Kane.

01:08:17.049 --> 01:08:19.007
We're all monsters, Benny boy.

01:08:24.404 --> 01:08:26.232
The difference is...

01:08:26.363 --> 01:08:27.973
[POURS DRINK]

01:08:28.104 --> 01:08:29.757
