01:08:29.888 --> 01:08:31.107
[SETS DOWN BOTTLE]

01:08:33.805 --> 01:08:35.285
Do you, Benny?

01:08:38.331 --> 01:08:40.464
Hey?

01:08:40.594 --> 01:08:42.205
Do ya, kid?

01:08:43.641 --> 01:08:45.599
