01:11:47.564 --> 01:11:49.435
or a monster.

01:11:49.566 --> 01:11:51.307
The choice is yours.

01:12:00.838 --> 01:12:03.493
Now, I will count to three.

01:12:03.623 --> 01:12:06.626
And if you're the man
that I think you are...

01:12:06.757 --> 01:12:09.281
